    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. Validation evidence demonstrates hemolysis index prediction error below 15% threshold across the operating envelope. The computational model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device in the pre-market submission context. No weakeners identified that would reduce confidence below the Medium assurance level threshold.",
